doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="public/styles/global.css")
    title Keranjang
    style.
      @media screen and (max-width:575px) {
        .keranjang-card-body {
          padding: 1em 0em !important;
        }
      }
  body
    main.container-fluid
      .row
        .col-md-6.border.ps-5.pe-5
          h3.w-75.border-bottom.fw-bold.py-4.mb-5 Keranjangku
          each i in [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
            .card.mb-3.border-0(style="max-width: 100%;")
              .row.g-0
                .col-sm-4
                  img.img-fluid.rounded-start(src="https://imageplaceholder.net/600", alt="img")
                .col-sm-8.border-bottom
                  .card-body.h-100.d-flex.pt-0.flex-column.justify-content-between.keranjang-card-body
                    h5.card-title.fw-bold.text-wrap Rengginang khas pulau penyengat, mix terasi udang
                    p.card-text.text-wrap.fs-6 quisquam facilis eos, quas sequi vero. Aspernatur eius fuga minima.
                    .d-flex.flex-wrap.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                      h6 Rp 36.000
                        span.px-3 X
                      .row.px-3
                        .col.border.py-2.rounded-1.text-center.py-1.px-3 -
                        .col.border.py-2.text-center.mx-2.rounded-1.py-1.px-3 1
                        .col.border.py-2.rounded-1.text-center.py-1.px-3 +

        .col-md-6.border.ps-5.pe-5.background-biru-muda-50
          h3.w-75.border-bottom.fw-bold.py-4.mb-5 Data Pemesanan
          h5.mb-5.fw-bold Total :
            span.fw-bold Rp 1.600.000
          form
            .mb-3
              label.form-label.fw-medium(for="name") Nama
              input#name.form-control(type="text", placeholder="your name")
            .mb-3
              label.form-label.fw-medium(for="email") Email
              input#email.form-control(type="email", placeholder="name@example.com")
            .mb-3
              label.form-label.fw-medium(for="alamat") Alamat
              input#alamat.form-control(type="text", placeholder="Jalan Pramuka")
            .mb-3
              label.form-label.fw-medium(for="no-hp") No Hp
              input#no-hp.form-control(type="text", placeholder="0812039182")
            button.btn.btn-primary.background-biru-laut.text-white.w-100.mt-5.mb-3 Checkout
            p.text-wrap
              small Data pribadi Anda akan digunakan untuk memproses pesanan Anda, mendukung pengalaman Anda di seluruh situs web ini, dan untuk tujuan lain yang dijelaskan dalam kebijakan privasi kami. Garansi uang kembali 30 hari.
    script(src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js")
